{"tid":1214162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［理性討論］地鐵不合作行動嘅好處","createTime":"2019-06-13T03:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T06:09:40.000Z","uid":135306,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe292233189a9189ba9e7e9286058f99c77f58d","tid":1214162,"uid":135306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:40:34.000Z","msg":"［並唔係否定包立會嘅作用，只想學術性探討兩者不同嘅定位及作用。］<br />\n<br />\n1. 跌親 病倒係地鐵並不違法<br />\n<br />\n2. 直接重挫經濟 交通<br />\n<br />\n3. 地鐵有普通市民掩護 （如果佢地堅持返工）班狗唔可以亂用胡椒同拋催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n4. 攞到主動權 唔係話去金鐘冇用 但如果政府下下都拖你 下下都話第日再開會 好快只會愈嚟愈少人出到嚟<br />\n<br />\n利申： 理性討論，犯法嘢我絕對唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46902d8cbe0ee0b447eef32e995673c90774a410","tid":1214162,"uid":135306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:43:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ba0140812f0d17a5acf3755e93c118f363611ca","tid":1214162,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:44:28.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"c3848b772f95f75377243bc5b2d3e03d7d010132","tid":1214162,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:46:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58089462ffab7af81e7212d7686ec3cf19b026f8","tid":1214162,"uid":135306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:48:36.000Z","msg":"唔該巴打 有嘅請再加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e157027251bf4967c93c2815a4007e6fbd427a","tid":1214162,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:49:25.000Z","msg":"公司有人話：好激進囉阻住人返工"},{"pid":"de2e4eaf4defc6296943d7a2442b13bf3770918f","tid":1214162,"uid":6417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:49:35.000Z","msg":"整合有關6.12簽名網！希望各位可以入黎簽個名<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1214184\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1214184</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"191b7ba20dc5b109bd205dd0f858d70083cf7e7b","tid":1214162,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:50:07.000Z","msg":"星期六日<br />\n東鐵好多遊客拖晒篋<br />\n大家唔好阻到佢哋"},{"pid":"98f96f7cf451302d924c9825c84561fac8dda51a","tid":1214162,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"191b7ba20dc5b109bd205dd0f858d70083cf7e7b","tid":1214162,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:50:07.000Z","msg":"星期六日<br />\n東鐵好多遊客拖晒篋<br />\n大家唔好阻到佢哋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:50:18.000Z","msg":"認同請廣傳"},{"pid":"1b6a6d78453eb33e0ab16d2c88126efbdcb0b397","tid":1214162,"uid":186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:50:43.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">#智取 </span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">#和理非</span><span style=\"color: maroon;\">#勇武</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">兄弟爬山，各自修行。 <br />\nWhy not all?</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"d5bed15728d357f21f7156d548b790dfeea41f51","tid":1214162,"uid":42949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:51:21.000Z","msg":"想問一下 地鐵塞成點 有冇人答到<br />\n除左今朝返工果一個幾鐘之後就冇曬消息<br />\n如果你話長期塞住 有經濟影響我都同意<br />\n但如果咁短時間只不過係搞到班友返工慢一陣 真心唔明有咩用"},{"pid":"d79323858e47204b331debc1199e3cecf4260b9b","tid":1214162,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:54:30.000Z","msg":"就係要塞到大家返唔到工，風頭火勢仲學人講返工？公司啲錢就嚟俾人送返上去"},{"pid":"6045e499e624d3cf93e96d076ad667f99c1ad0ff","tid":1214162,"uid":135306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5bed15728d357f21f7156d548b790dfeea41f51","tid":1214162,"uid":42949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:51:21.000Z","msg":"想問一下 地鐵塞成點 有冇人答到<br />\n除左今朝返工果一個幾鐘之後就冇曬消息<br />\n如果你話長期塞住 有經濟影響我都同意<br />\n但如果咁短時間只不過係搞到班友返工慢一陣 真心唔明有咩用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"今日只係做到塞慢咗 人龍長咗<br />\n<br />\n但原因係因為今朝傳有機會開會 連登內部意見不一 所以先得好少人<br />\n<br />\n我會視今日為宣傳/ 示範嘅性質 至少引起咗媒體注意<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有一樣嘢：我相信呢個不合作運動應該會有更多和理非肯同敢做"},{"pid":"18657d21a5b3b8840369af90fef2ba80e2a4c8c6","tid":1214162,"uid":57566,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:57:58.000Z","msg":"係林鄭要硬過既時候<br />\n我覺得集中係立法會先<br />\n阻唔到 條例過左再搞地鐵"},{"pid":"ce0e3682233297eb20c4dc44a0cb20a10f05ec98","tid":1214162,"uid":46896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:00:04.000Z","msg":"好處係門檻低，只要有合理理由坐地鐵，黑警唔可以拉你。呢啲野唔同去金鐘衝同食 tear gas，塞地鐵只要你有時間就做到"},{"pid":"2c704d13215dc9be53076a2e1d3a80df046d92fd","tid":1214162,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:23:36.000Z","msg":"留言跟進"},{"pid":"7655887f3a1ade32f7d04b320397678b394e044e","tid":1214162,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:25:25.000Z","msg":"今朝交通時間多咗十五分鐘 成效好似唔多夠<br />\n要再多啲人塞"},{"pid":"8d108d4857c44c7da1c7660e8a2a7047aec8425b","tid":1214162,"uid":123274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6e14ce68d9bb8ae88fe76268acaa02072d527f","tid":1214162,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:09:01.000Z","msg":"其實香港仲有一班人係中立同仲同情班學生<br />\n<br />\n如果你地搞死佢地無得番工&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nd民意會開始流入建制派 轉而支持政府<br />\n解決呢班認為我地搞事既人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重申?運動不但要令政府覺得驚&nbsp;<br />\n但同時要贏形象&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n要係利益中平衡&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n先至唔會比政府有機會有籍口搵位入你<br />\n<br />\n好似昨天咁 磚頭合理化左警察既武力<br />\n令到林鄭用呢個point入我地<br />\n<br />\n希望大家過左今日唔好再搞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉而支持超合作運動&nbsp;"},{"pid":"124315a160901fe7b1aa29c047c5530a28922595","tid":1214162,"uid":22894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:09:40.000Z","msg":"呢個係來自一班鐵膠嘅呼籲<br />\n無論你搭咩車 點搭車 都要摸清楚緊急設備 <br />\n免得出起事來累人累己<br />\n拿 唔係緊急唔好用呀 一個唔該半個鐘都無車到<br />\n影響大家翻工就麻鳩煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DHPEtk5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDHPEtk5.png&h=e0650ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zs39Qzu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZs39Qzu.png&h=3d5a172e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GNetmF8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGNetmF8.png&h=6a8ffb00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P0qwjsM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP0qwjsM.png&h=ddd4ac0a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/90M7Cew.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F90M7Cew.png&h=40abe25d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sBp5oUx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsBp5oUx.png&h=7917b9f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H1PMSNN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH1PMSNN.png&h=d9ef5a4e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}